      "content": "thanks for that. that's super helpful. specifically with the latino one you mentioned—about them being \"criminal\" or \"passionate\"—can you give me some more detail on how that actually looks on screen? like, what are some specific character archetypes or traits that usually define those roles in movies? i want to make sure i'm getting the nuances right for the parody.",
